title: Tokyo-Listed European stock ETF falls 0.3 percent after Italian elections
text: Home / NEWS / Tokyo-Listed European stock ETF falls 0.3 percent after Italian elections Tokyo-Listed European stock ETF falls 0.3 percent after Italian elections 8 hours ago NEWS , tokyo TOKYO, March 5 (Reuters) – Tokyo-Listed Euro Stoxx 50 ETF fell 0.3 percent in early Monday trade after early counting pointed to a strong showing by Italy’s anti-establishment 5-Star Movement and the anti-immigration League party. Reporting by Hideyuki Sano; Editing by Kim Coghill Our Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles.
